short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Voting records of Australian Elected Officials

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A tool that augments the Facebook pages of Australian politicians, highlighting the policies they've voted for and against. An attempt to make politicians more accountable to what they say online.
